    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras/1b8893c07df563d5d20e4daf14a3096f.avif?t=1728524507\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras_big/1b8893c07df563d5d20e4daf14a3096f.avif?t=1728524507 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a quiet and peaceful journey in Along long road!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You should be thoroughly prepared when walking toward a long, long road. That way you can see the end of this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras/8a1a9e6aa53cd8a30d7d50d4e7ccb082.avif?t=1728524507\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras_big/8a1a9e6aa53cd8a30d7d50d4e7ccb082.avif?t=1728524507 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player take the tent and money and walk towards the end of the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Red Rooftop shops sell various items for travel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These items will be of great help to your trip.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can relax and cook at the campsite in the middle of the street.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Highly recommend the food I get from cooking because it can fill my hunger more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras/f7dc960fc9a4ae4f692834e161ce5711.avif?t=1728524507\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras_big/f7dc960fc9a4ae4f692834e161ce5711.avif?t=1728524507 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras/c9214c841d85d210e47d1de8545db644.avif?t=1728524507\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras_big/c9214c841d85d210e47d1de8545db644.avif?t=1728524507 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras/56d260cab298d4aa6a4591c69e378895.avif?t=1728524507\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251070/extras_big/56d260cab298d4aa6a4591c69e378895.avif?t=1728524507 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will walk the path of various environments. ( Forests, lakes with horizontal views, dry deserts, etc )</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also, you can know the distance, weather, and time you walked on your phone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The goal of this game is to walk a long way and reach the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player cannot save the progress because there is no checkpoint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no automatic movement, so you have to be patient and move forward yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finally, what's at the end of this road?</p>",
